wiki.content: Singer/rapper/songwriter/producer Cee Lo Green scored a huge hit single with 'Forget You' in October 2010 – sales of the clean version and the slightly in your face, “N.S.F.W.” version were combined for chart purposes and the single shot to the top spot to give Cee Lo his first solo UK No.1. wiki.summary: Singer/rapper/songwriter/producer Cee Lo Green scored a huge hit single with 'Forget You' in October 2010 – sales of the clean version and the slightly in your face, “N.S.F.W.” version were combined for chart purposes and the single shot to the top spot to give Cee Lo his first solo UK No.1.
